WEBVTT

01:35.700 --> 01:39.980
[Veil of Shadows]

01:39.980 --> 01:42.980
[Episode 11]

02:16.910 --> 02:17.940
Why is my magic gone?

02:22.840 --> 02:23.660
Wu Shiguang?

02:28.240 --> 02:28.980
Let's talk inside.

02:46.800 --> 02:48.130
Why'd you grab a kid?

02:52.240 --> 02:53.260
I found him in the river.

02:56.400 --> 02:57.130
Want some tea?

02:58.000 --> 02:58.730
Pour it yourself.

03:04.800 --> 03:06.100
What's going on?

03:06.430 --> 03:07.380
Where are we exactly?

03:09.190 --> 03:10.850
In an old illusion inside the Star Stone.

03:11.430 --> 03:12.450
And now we're living

03:12.840 --> 03:14.260
as people from the past.

03:16.430 --> 03:17.260
An illusion?

03:18.400 --> 03:19.950
Did your master tell you that?

03:27.000 --> 03:27.780
Why does your master

03:28.240 --> 03:29.820
know the Star Stone so well?

03:30.710 --> 03:31.820
My master understands

03:32.360 --> 03:33.170
all things in the world.

03:33.870 --> 03:34.940
And he taught me a lot.

03:35.080 --> 03:35.890
Alright.

03:37.030 --> 03:38.100
Then where's my partner?

03:39.870 --> 03:41.260
Probably the same as us,

03:42.360 --> 03:43.170
but maybe

03:43.960 --> 03:45.290
she's in a different past.

03:46.710 --> 03:47.610
I just hope

03:47.630 --> 03:48.980
she got a better family.

03:51.280 --> 03:52.780
This one's way too poor.

03:53.310 --> 03:54.170
This family has

03:54.190 --> 03:55.010
such bad luck.

03:56.680 --> 03:58.260
So how do we leave this illusion?

03:58.640 --> 03:59.940
We need the Star Stone here

04:00.050 --> 04:01.310
to leave the illusion.

04:02.480 --> 04:04.690
But it is the Aodeng tribe's treasure.

04:05.440 --> 04:06.420
It's hidden away.

04:06.910 --> 04:07.780
Only the chieftain

04:08.120 --> 04:09.130
knows where it is.

04:10.630 --> 04:11.500
That's easy.

04:12.910 --> 04:13.940
Di Zhu's father

04:14.120 --> 04:15.340
will be back in three days.

04:15.960 --> 04:17.450
We can ask him using Word Magic.

04:18.710 --> 04:19.980
Besides, you said

04:20.070 --> 04:21.060
a hundred years here

04:21.120 --> 04:22.220
is just a moment out there.

04:23.720 --> 04:24.980
Staying here a couple of days

04:25.630 --> 04:26.490
should be fine, right?

04:29.430 --> 04:30.100
Hey, Know-Something,

04:30.390 --> 04:31.490
how much longer can you hold on?

04:31.720 --> 04:33.290
Seems like it could break any moment!

04:35.200 --> 04:36.420
You called me Know-It-All earlier.

04:37.510 --> 04:39.100
Now it's Know-Something?

04:39.900 --> 04:40.790
Maybe he thinks

04:40.790 --> 04:42.540
you're weaker than you look.

04:42.750 --> 04:44.100
He's just trying to stir trouble, Master Bai Ze.

04:44.720 --> 04:45.580
Don't listen to him.

04:47.040 --> 04:48.050
You look really worn out.

04:48.560 --> 04:49.540
Is there anything I can do?

04:50.270 --> 04:51.590
The illusion inside the Star Stone

04:51.750 --> 04:53.730
flows at a different speed than we do.

04:54.430 --> 04:55.660
A thousand days inside

04:56.160 --> 04:57.140
is just a blink out here.

04:58.190 --> 04:58.810
So,

04:59.510 --> 05:01.020
even if I can only hold on for a short while,

05:01.480 --> 05:03.170
I can buy them a hundred years inside.

05:03.910 --> 05:04.810
Bai Ze,

05:05.600 --> 05:07.170
you know everything in the world.

05:07.680 --> 05:08.730
How could you forget

05:09.120 --> 05:10.780
the disasters that happened here?

05:12.120 --> 05:12.730
Disasters?

05:13.190 --> 05:13.900
What disasters?

05:14.360 --> 05:15.780
Goddess Nuwa once prophesied

05:15.920 --> 05:17.540
that four disasters would strike here:

05:18.310 --> 05:20.170
a great fire that burns everything,

05:20.800 --> 05:22.220
a devastating storm that destroys the world,

05:22.590 --> 05:24.240
a meteor shower that levels all,

05:24.720 --> 05:25.370
and

05:26.120 --> 05:27.610
a deadly freeze that withers all life.

05:28.160 --> 05:30.300
The first disaster, the great fire,

05:30.630 --> 05:32.100
was the heavenly fire

05:32.120 --> 05:33.200
brought by the falling star.

05:33.750 --> 05:34.900
After that,

05:35.800 --> 05:37.450
the other three disasters

05:37.870 --> 05:39.100
all happened too.

05:39.360 --> 05:40.790
The guys inside the Star Stone

05:42.160 --> 05:43.580
are not far

05:44.560 --> 05:45.490
from these disasters.

05:46.430 --> 05:48.100
So their time

05:49.040 --> 05:49.730
is running out.

05:51.020 --> 05:58.230
[Seven days until the Hurricane Catastrophe, 1000 years ago]

05:58.230 --> 05:58.780
Oh, right.

05:59.830 --> 06:01.530
The stone paintings said

06:01.960 --> 06:03.810
you and I are bound by a troubled fate.

06:04.360 --> 06:06.020
If we get married successfully,

06:06.520 --> 06:08.370
then the Star Stone will be my dowry,

06:08.750 --> 06:09.530
right in our hands.

06:10.160 --> 06:11.660
It's Man Man marrying Di Zhu.

06:12.480 --> 06:14.290
We're Man Man and Di Zhu now.

06:15.480 --> 06:16.580
We're fated ones.

06:16.950 --> 06:18.170
We're a pair wherever we go.

06:19.830 --> 06:21.290
Isn't your fated one

06:22.480 --> 06:23.410
Ji Ling?

06:27.310 --> 06:27.930
You've muttered about him

06:28.480 --> 06:29.660
countless times in your dreams.

06:33.870 --> 06:34.900
How do you know?

06:38.120 --> 06:39.410
Did you sneak a peek at me at night?

06:41.540 --> 06:45.140
♪They say if we loved once before♪

06:45.700 --> 06:47.900
♪Even apart, we still feel it all♪

06:48.300 --> 06:53.300
♪Like thousands of blooms on that shore♪

06:54.300 --> 06:57.620
♪At last, the moment is here♪

06:57.940 --> 07:02.580
♪You smile at me, but it's bittersweet♪

07:03.060 --> 07:06.020
♪Still, not a word I hear...♪

07:06.040 --> 07:06.700
Ji Ling...

07:11.000 --> 07:11.980
my fated one...

07:13.980 --> 07:15.740
♪Watch the moon rise, wait for daylight to go♪

07:15.900 --> 07:19.700
♪Back to back, we lost ourselves in time we let go♪

07:19.940 --> 07:26.300
♪Till snow falls deep, turning mountains to homes♪

07:26.900 --> 07:28.460
♪I know you're waiting for me♪

07:28.580 --> 07:32.060
♪With flowers in hand, I'm on my way to you♪

07:34.480 --> 07:35.490
I'm not Ji Ling.

07:36.920 --> 07:38.290
Your seduction tricks

07:38.800 --> 07:39.700
won't work on me.

07:42.510 --> 07:43.660
Ji Ling once said that too.

07:51.430 --> 07:53.810
You can wear any skin you want,

07:55.450 --> 07:58.050
but your heart can't be faked.

08:02.800 --> 08:03.810
What you see now

08:05.310 --> 08:06.220
is all fake.

08:07.310 --> 08:08.290
Don't get too deep into the act.

08:09.480 --> 08:11.020
But to get the Star Stone,

08:11.630 --> 08:12.930
you really do have to marry me.

08:21.070 --> 08:22.370
See, you're practically drooling.

08:23.070 --> 08:23.700
Come on,

08:24.390 --> 08:25.100
have a taste.

08:25.680 --> 08:26.410
It smells so good.

08:30.240 --> 08:30.980
One more time:

08:32.070 --> 08:33.100
I'm a vegetarian.

08:34.720 --> 08:35.810
Quit pretending.

08:36.630 --> 08:37.340
Fine, don't eat then.

09:04.460 --> 09:14.140
[Twenty-four hours until the Meteor Blast, 150 years ago]

09:14.360 --> 09:14.850
Yuan Xizai,

09:15.320 --> 09:16.340
what are you even doing?

09:16.360 --> 09:17.950
Your mind-control tricks

09:18.240 --> 09:19.100
won't work on me!

09:19.550 --> 09:20.650
Today's our only chance

09:20.650 --> 09:21.830
to get the Star Stone.

09:21.910 --> 09:22.940
Time's running out.

09:23.080 --> 09:24.150
Stop messing around!

09:30.360 --> 09:31.060
How is he?

09:33.120 --> 09:33.650
Put it on!

09:36.120 --> 09:36.730
He hit his head.

09:37.360 --> 09:37.940
He should be fine.

09:51.030 --> 09:52.580
This is Green Ape territory?

09:53.320 --> 09:54.010
Yeah.

09:55.670 --> 09:56.580
We just wiped out

09:56.720 --> 09:58.420
the human reinforcements stationed here.

09:59.720 --> 10:00.420
We...

10:02.440 --> 10:03.610
wiped out humans?

10:06.200 --> 10:07.220
We're not human?

10:08.390 --> 10:09.010
We are...

10:12.480 --> 10:13.730
high-rank Green Ape demons.

10:22.340 --> 10:28.140
[Fifty years until the Great Freeze, 100 years ago]

10:28.150 --> 10:29.700
So where do we look for the Star Stone?

10:31.670 --> 10:32.340
I don't know.

10:33.960 --> 10:35.580
Besides what my master told me,

10:36.200 --> 10:37.180
in my memory,

10:37.910 --> 10:39.770
the Star Stone never appeared.

10:41.840 --> 10:42.530
But that's okay.

10:43.870 --> 10:45.010
We have enough time.

10:50.750 --> 10:51.580
For what?

10:58.840 --> 10:59.730
Finding the Star Stone.

11:01.030 --> 11:01.850
Wu Zhiqi,

11:02.320 --> 11:04.060
if they don't get the real Star Stone,

11:05.150 --> 11:06.010
then its power

11:06.030 --> 11:07.060
won't be activated.

11:08.000 --> 11:08.820
And your people

11:09.600 --> 11:11.180
will just keep sleeping.

11:12.120 --> 11:13.180
You're lying to me.

11:14.030 --> 11:15.490
If even I can lie,

11:16.270 --> 11:17.700
then there's no truth in this world.

11:18.480 --> 11:19.100
Master Bai Ze,

11:19.910 --> 11:21.460
you know all things.

11:22.750 --> 11:24.010
You must have another way, right?

11:25.320 --> 11:26.530
There is indeed one more way.

11:28.000 --> 11:29.060
A place might connect

11:29.840 --> 11:31.530
to the Star Stone illusion.

11:32.360 --> 11:33.420
But to open the exit,

11:34.120 --> 11:35.180
we need someone's blood.

11:35.600 --> 11:36.010
Whose?

11:37.030 --> 11:38.370
I'll rally my weasels...

11:38.750 --> 11:39.250
I mean,

11:40.360 --> 11:41.220
my Weasel brothers.

11:41.510 --> 11:42.300
Wherever he is,

11:42.440 --> 11:43.530
I'll find him

11:43.720 --> 11:44.370
and bleed him dry.

11:44.960 --> 11:45.610
Just say the name.

11:46.120 --> 11:46.770
Leave the rest

11:47.750 --> 11:48.580
to me.

11:49.030 --> 11:49.650
Wu Shiguang.

11:52.440 --> 11:53.010
Hey, Know-Nothing.

11:53.960 --> 11:54.770
Are you serious?

11:58.670 --> 11:59.220
Got it!

11:59.790 --> 12:01.180
I know where to find Wu Shiguang's blood!

12:01.360 --> 12:02.300
You're up, You Chi.

12:02.790 --> 12:03.850
Get Wu Shiguang's blood,

12:04.480 --> 12:05.820
then risk opening the exit.

12:06.750 --> 12:07.730
Risk it?

12:09.600 --> 12:10.490
All by myself?

12:49.240 --> 12:49.940
So,

12:50.080 --> 12:51.650
we're a married couple now.

12:53.320 --> 12:54.010
That's right.

12:54.870 --> 12:55.940
I'm the chief of the Flood Dragon clan,

12:56.750 --> 12:57.460
named Cang Hao.

12:59.000 --> 12:59.820
You're my...

13:03.910 --> 13:04.460
wife.

13:05.630 --> 13:06.460
Your name's Qing Yi.

13:06.750 --> 13:07.820
Got it, Darling.

13:09.240 --> 13:10.650
You call it "darling" here, right?

13:16.960 --> 13:18.650
This child is different from others here.

13:18.910 --> 13:19.770
It has no horns.

13:20.840 --> 13:22.340
Let's see if it's a boy or girl.

13:22.480 --> 13:23.130
No need to look.

13:23.960 --> 13:24.340
It's a boy.

13:25.140 --> 13:26.430
How do you know?

13:27.240 --> 13:28.100
How can you be sure?

13:28.750 --> 13:29.550
- How do you... - It's me!

13:30.000 --> 13:30.850
It... it's me!

13:32.080 --> 13:32.820
Wu Shiguang!

13:50.510 --> 13:51.340
Shiguang baby.

13:53.750 --> 13:54.980
Can you not call him that?

13:56.440 --> 13:57.250
Then what should I call him?

13:57.960 --> 13:59.740
I'm little Shiguang's mother now.

14:00.000 --> 14:01.130
I'll call him whatever I want.

14:01.790 --> 14:03.220
You're lucky I didn't go with "Brat."

14:05.720 --> 14:06.490
Hi, Brat...

14:09.440 --> 14:11.340
This illusion is really something.

14:12.270 --> 14:13.580
I'm your mother now?

14:14.720 --> 14:15.770
Is it because grown-up you

14:15.790 --> 14:16.580
is so annoying,

14:17.200 --> 14:19.250
so you send little Shiguang

14:19.670 --> 14:20.980
to make yourself look a little better?

14:22.030 --> 14:23.060
What's wrong with grown-up me?

14:24.600 --> 14:25.220
Not handsome enough?

14:26.720 --> 14:27.700
The looks are okay.

14:28.870 --> 14:29.820
The personality, though...

14:32.030 --> 14:32.850
went a bit crooked.

14:41.240 --> 14:42.340
If you see a demon

14:43.080 --> 14:44.940
with a heart-shaped, wavy birthmark,

14:45.840 --> 14:47.490
bring them back immediately.

14:50.600 --> 14:52.130
Your birthmark is pretty interesting.

14:52.910 --> 14:54.460
Looks like a heart made of flowing water.

14:55.840 --> 14:57.220
How come I never noticed it before?

14:57.960 --> 14:59.250
I wear a painted skin to hide my identity,

14:59.910 --> 15:01.130
so others can't see it.

15:11.270 --> 15:12.180
Where are you going?

15:15.240 --> 15:16.580
To find the Star Stone, of course.

15:17.960 --> 15:19.220
Or do you really plan

15:19.390 --> 15:20.820
to stay here with me like a loving couple,

15:21.200 --> 15:21.980
grow old together?

15:23.840 --> 15:24.700
What about the kid?

15:25.840 --> 15:26.490
Put him to sleep,

15:26.720 --> 15:27.370
feed him,

15:27.450 --> 15:28.180
change his diapers.

15:29.000 --> 15:29.850
I can't do any of that!

15:30.510 --> 15:32.100
Isn't your master all-knowing?

15:32.600 --> 15:33.530
Didn't he teach you?

15:35.030 --> 15:36.130
Wake up.

15:37.000 --> 15:37.980
This is an illusion.

15:38.630 --> 15:39.820
Just leave him here.

15:40.150 --> 15:40.850
He won't die.

15:41.600 --> 15:43.180
How can you be so cold?

15:44.120 --> 15:44.650
Let him go,

15:44.750 --> 15:46.130
and let us go too, okay?

15:46.600 --> 15:47.700
Business first.

15:50.670 --> 15:51.220
No way!

15:52.030 --> 15:53.220
Isn't it all fake anyway?

15:54.910 --> 15:55.580
Still no!

16:19.330 --> 16:20.430
Bai Ze said

16:20.510 --> 16:21.880
lighting this talisman

16:21.880 --> 16:22.570
is all it takes.

16:23.240 --> 16:23.850
Don't worry.

16:24.550 --> 16:25.700
I'll send two people to protect you.

16:27.120 --> 16:27.770
Where are my helpers?

16:28.840 --> 16:29.650
Where are my bodyguards?

16:52.980 --> 16:56.080
[Jin Zheng, Pojun, the Northern Dipper Hunter]

16:56.080 --> 16:56.730
Watch out!

17:03.260 --> 17:06.660
[Hua Qi, Tiantong, the Southern Dipper Hunter]

17:15.550 --> 17:16.980
Didn't expect to find one here.

17:17.240 --> 17:18.050
This trip was worth it.

17:18.480 --> 17:19.380
Is that something to be proud of?

17:20.030 --> 17:20.860
After a whole month,

17:21.350 --> 17:22.700
we just stumbled upon one by accident.

17:23.790 --> 17:24.660
I miss the days

17:25.110 --> 17:26.810
working with Senior Si Feng.

17:27.920 --> 17:29.180
The new generation surpasses the old.

17:29.550 --> 17:30.940
Appreciate who's in front of you, okay?

17:32.000 --> 17:33.220
Besides, how am I worse than her?

17:33.750 --> 17:34.490
You're worse

17:35.590 --> 17:36.530
in any way.

17:39.110 --> 17:40.140
You're such a bad senior.

17:41.400 --> 17:41.860
Stop right there!

17:47.830 --> 17:49.010
I'm just a low-rank demon.

17:49.080 --> 17:50.610
I haven't done anything terrible.

17:51.030 --> 17:51.530
At most,

17:51.640 --> 17:52.860
I steal a chicken now and then.

17:53.480 --> 17:55.430
Please, honored double-flower hunters,

17:56.110 --> 17:57.010
go easy on me.

18:00.830 --> 18:02.330
Bai Ze did ask us to protect you,

18:03.110 --> 18:03.700
but

18:04.480 --> 18:05.770
you don't have to bow so low.

18:13.350 --> 18:14.900
What? Master Bai Ze sent us here

18:15.750 --> 18:16.980
to rob a grave?

18:19.160 --> 18:20.470
Who would just save someone's blood

18:20.470 --> 18:21.240
for no reason?

18:21.480 --> 18:22.660
Even for a close friend,

18:23.550 --> 18:24.700
that's pretty weird.

18:26.000 --> 18:27.900
When you first joined the Shilin Sect,

18:28.640 --> 18:30.010
you took evil demons' heads,

18:30.070 --> 18:30.850
claws,

18:31.000 --> 18:31.620
and teeth

18:31.720 --> 18:32.420
as trophies,

18:32.720 --> 18:33.460
filling your whole room.

18:33.960 --> 18:34.700
Sometimes,

18:35.310 --> 18:36.220
you even slept hugging them.

18:36.640 --> 18:37.730
If we're talking weird...

18:39.440 --> 18:41.420
Hey, great double-flower hunters,

18:42.270 --> 18:43.660
you just stand there and watch?

18:44.270 --> 18:45.290
Don't your consciences bother you?

18:45.720 --> 18:47.290
Is this how Bai Ze told you to help me?

18:48.000 --> 18:48.810
What he said was

18:49.480 --> 18:50.220
to protect you.

18:51.200 --> 18:51.730
Helping you

18:52.510 --> 18:53.380
costs extra.

19:08.830 --> 19:10.180
Why are you stealing from the dead?

19:11.160 --> 19:12.290
This is my own stuff.

19:14.270 --> 19:16.070
You buried it here for yourself in advance?

19:16.310 --> 19:17.050
Nonsense!

19:19.350 --> 19:19.860
This is the first thing

19:20.240 --> 19:21.530
I ever stole from the human world

19:22.480 --> 19:24.380
when I turned sixteen.

19:25.480 --> 19:26.220
For us weasels,

19:26.240 --> 19:28.300
the first thing we steal is extremely important!

19:28.550 --> 19:30.490
It represents our name for life!

19:30.720 --> 19:31.900
Look what you stole.

19:32.270 --> 19:33.250
A ruler!

19:33.880 --> 19:35.170
Look what Wu Shiguang did!

19:35.270 --> 19:35.700
Father,

19:35.880 --> 19:37.140
don't expect me to be a legend.

19:37.480 --> 19:38.980
He's on another level.

19:39.160 --> 19:39.730
I can't match that.

19:40.030 --> 19:40.660
Besides,

19:40.960 --> 19:42.380
I'm just a little weasel.

19:43.640 --> 19:44.860
Stealing a ruler isn't so bad.

19:45.310 --> 19:46.530
You only stole a cane yourself.

19:46.550 --> 19:47.490
You dare talk back?

19:50.830 --> 19:52.570
Our weasel family motto is:

19:53.270 --> 19:54.010
Do your best.

19:54.590 --> 19:55.700
Don't force it.

19:56.310 --> 19:59.090
As long as you have no regrets.

20:03.350 --> 20:04.180
I'll never forget

20:05.310 --> 20:06.010
your kindness in raising me.

20:07.160 --> 20:08.330
But I have to avenge

20:09.200 --> 20:09.940
this blood debt.

20:10.720 --> 20:12.290
So I must venture into the human world.

20:13.680 --> 20:14.140
Sir,

20:16.310 --> 20:16.810
take care.

20:21.440 --> 20:22.050
You brat,

20:22.440 --> 20:23.090
don't do anything reckless.

20:23.550 --> 20:25.050
The human world is very dangerous.

20:25.660 --> 20:27.580
♪The quiet tears can overflow♪

20:27.620 --> 20:31.540
♪Life rolls on, like thunder in a dream...♪

20:35.110 --> 20:35.810
Don't worry.

20:36.100 --> 20:38.380
♪Even our weakness, we believe...♪

20:38.790 --> 20:39.490
Listen,

20:40.000 --> 20:41.570
no fighting while I'm away.

20:42.000 --> 20:43.140
Don't worry your father.

20:43.680 --> 20:44.290
Off you go.

20:45.880 --> 20:46.530
Go...

20:47.900 --> 20:53.380
♪Childhood passion, grown-up dreams...♪

20:54.070 --> 20:54.660
Go...

20:55.700 --> 20:58.060
♪In the night, a boy's soft cry♪

20:58.420 --> 21:01.180
♪Heartbeats racing, asking why♪

21:03.100 --> 21:05.860
♪In the wind, a swaying glow♪

21:05.860 --> 21:08.380
♪Just a little lantern in the cold♪

21:12.350 --> 21:13.770
I'm worried about you.

21:13.920 --> 21:14.700
Let me go with you!

21:17.640 --> 21:19.140
But the human world is very dangerous.

21:19.270 --> 21:19.700
That's right.

21:20.070 --> 21:21.010
So I'm going with you.

21:21.270 --> 21:22.090
With us together,

21:22.510 --> 21:23.770
this very dangerous human world

21:24.550 --> 21:25.730
is only half as dangerous for you!

21:28.720 --> 21:29.180
Besides,

21:30.240 --> 21:31.620
I've even made us

21:31.640 --> 21:32.420
a cool partnership name.

21:33.510 --> 21:34.420
We'll be...

21:35.200 --> 21:36.140
the Wu-Chi Duo!

21:40.590 --> 21:41.050
How about that?

21:42.550 --> 21:43.380
Where's your ruler?

21:46.350 --> 21:47.240
I left it with my father.

21:47.680 --> 21:48.510
In case he misses me.

21:48.790 --> 21:49.940
Seeing it is like seeing me.

21:51.260 --> 21:57.820
♪Up the hill, arms open wide, we sing♪

21:58.220 --> 22:04.580
♪You and me, we fear not a thing♪

22:06.020 --> 22:12.540
♪Life may sigh, but with our flesh and bone♪

22:12.980 --> 22:18.700
♪We brave the storm, and claim the truths we own♪

22:24.480 --> 22:25.980
Behind those shifty eyes,

22:26.680 --> 22:27.570
you're so loyal?

22:28.030 --> 22:28.660
Of course!

22:31.510 --> 22:32.180
Hey,

22:33.270 --> 22:35.860
these are big, bright eyes!

22:39.960 --> 22:40.700
Found it.

22:41.030 --> 22:41.660
That's it.

22:43.310 --> 22:44.980
An enchanted animal trap.

22:46.310 --> 22:46.940
Watch out!

22:48.750 --> 22:49.290
Wu Shiguang!

22:52.000 --> 22:52.620
Your leg!

22:55.200 --> 22:56.490
Thanks to Wu Shiguang pushing me away,

22:57.480 --> 22:58.180
or I'd be dead.

22:59.680 --> 23:00.530
But back then,

23:00.830 --> 23:01.750
out of nowhere,

23:01.750 --> 23:03.180
a ball of white light suddenly appeared

23:03.400 --> 23:04.570
and protected Wu Shiguang.

23:06.350 --> 23:07.090
So he didn't die either.

23:07.640 --> 23:10.010
We're really buddies in misfortune.

23:10.160 --> 23:11.050
Enough with the talk now?

23:12.350 --> 23:13.050
Delay any longer,

23:13.480 --> 23:14.810
your buddy might run into real misfortune.

23:50.160 --> 23:50.860
What are you doing?

23:51.240 --> 23:52.010
Humming.

23:52.590 --> 23:53.250
Do you like it?

23:58.350 --> 23:59.250
He probably likes it.

24:01.880 --> 24:02.660
He's you.

24:03.510 --> 24:04.940
You like it.

24:05.720 --> 24:06.620
Do you like me...

24:08.750 --> 24:09.420
humming?

24:14.680 --> 24:15.620
Getting shy already?

24:16.350 --> 24:17.490
Then what will you do when we sleep

24:17.490 --> 24:18.010
without clothes tonight?

24:18.030 --> 24:18.530
Nonsense!

24:19.680 --> 24:20.380
What decent person

24:20.440 --> 24:21.180
sleeps without clothes?

24:28.480 --> 24:29.140
Don't come closer.

24:38.000 --> 24:39.420
We each have our own quilt,

24:39.680 --> 24:40.810
and it's thicker than anything.

24:42.510 --> 24:44.140
I'm a girl and I don't even mind.

24:44.680 --> 24:45.770
And you're complaining?

24:49.000 --> 24:50.630
I saw you couldn't sleep,

24:50.680 --> 24:51.960
so I'm just keeping you company.

25:02.200 --> 25:02.860
This place...

25:04.200 --> 25:05.330
was once my home,

25:06.830 --> 25:08.290
with my happiest memories,

25:10.030 --> 25:11.330
my dearest family,

25:13.030 --> 25:14.290
and everything from my childhood.

25:17.680 --> 25:19.490
Even knowing this is an illusion,

25:20.680 --> 25:22.620
I'm still overwhelmed by mixed emotions.

25:25.630 --> 25:26.940
It's like having

25:28.630 --> 25:29.660
a very, very...

25:31.230 --> 25:32.290
sad dream.

25:33.550 --> 25:35.140
When I saw that baby in the swaddle,

25:36.270 --> 25:37.770
moonlight shining on him.

25:38.550 --> 25:39.570
I recalled my father said

25:41.030 --> 25:42.420
he named me Shiguang
[* "Shiguang" means "finding a light"]

25:43.510 --> 25:45.180
because the day he found me,

25:46.160 --> 25:47.090
it was like finding

25:47.680 --> 25:48.860
a light that brought them

25:49.350 --> 25:50.290
warmth and joy.

25:52.590 --> 25:54.090
He hoped my future

25:57.000 --> 25:58.090
to be colorful,

26:00.000 --> 26:01.010
peaceful and bright.

26:10.000 --> 26:11.050
So you want to stay

26:11.270 --> 26:12.900
and take care of this child,

26:14.270 --> 26:15.860
just like your father and mother

26:16.590 --> 26:17.700
took care of you.

26:42.070 --> 26:43.330
My mother never slept well,

26:44.880 --> 26:45.770
always had nightmares.

26:48.000 --> 26:49.420
I remember my father, just like this,

26:50.830 --> 26:52.420
would gently pat her shoulder.

27:06.310 --> 27:07.660
Let's look for the Star Stone tomorrow.

27:48.100 --> 27:51.540
♪If there's a little village down the road♪

27:52.260 --> 27:54.500
♪By a river bending soft and slow♪

27:54.900 --> 27:59.860
♪You hum a tune by the fire's glow♪

28:00.740 --> 28:04.100
♪Time would linger, never go♪

28:04.500 --> 28:09.100
♪Even the wind would fade, just you and me♪

28:09.620 --> 28:12.860
♪Hand in hand, we'd sit close, quietly♪

28:13.700 --> 28:20.180
♪Watch the years ripple, row by row♪

28:20.540 --> 28:25.860
♪You say a hug keeps hearts from growing old♪

28:26.380 --> 28:32.980
♪Save up for a place of our own♪

28:33.300 --> 28:39.220
♪Plant wildflowers till the whole field's grown♪

28:59.700 --> 29:04.420
♪Sing and sway, you laugh along with me♪

29:11.700 --> 29:17.260
♪Keep this corner, our sweet little home♪

29:17.700 --> 29:24.100
♪You're the brightest moon I know♪

29:24.460 --> 29:30.020
♪Sweetest berry that ever grew♪

29:30.460 --> 29:36.820
♪I was a drifter on the road♪

29:37.260 --> 29:42.980
♪Till you gave me a story to hold♪

30:10.110 --> 30:10.770
Man Man!

30:12.240 --> 30:12.770
Wake up!

30:13.000 --> 30:13.660
Get up!

30:14.310 --> 30:14.810
What's wrong?

30:15.440 --> 30:16.140
We've got a problem.

30:17.000 --> 30:17.460
Let's go.

30:37.160 --> 30:38.940
How dare you cancel my wedding with Man Man?

30:39.350 --> 30:40.050
Di Zhu,

30:40.790 --> 30:42.330
ever since Man Man came here,

30:42.830 --> 30:44.420
three of our people have died!

30:45.000 --> 30:46.140
Such a bringer of disaster

30:46.480 --> 30:47.290
cannot stay!

30:47.920 --> 30:48.980
My father is the chieftain.

30:49.310 --> 30:50.090
He's the one who decides.

30:50.350 --> 30:50.810
You...

30:52.720 --> 30:53.620
When did you become

30:53.640 --> 30:54.900
so disrespectful?

30:55.350 --> 30:57.010
Sir, please give me three more days.

30:57.510 --> 30:58.220
Within three days,

30:58.830 --> 30:59.940
I will find the real killer

31:00.400 --> 31:01.180
and prove my innocence.

31:01.960 --> 31:02.770
And if you don't?

31:04.070 --> 31:05.570
Then burn Man Man alive.

31:09.550 --> 31:10.250
Burn me too.

31:11.200 --> 31:12.180
I'll die with him!

31:14.110 --> 31:15.050
Touched, huh?

31:25.480 --> 31:26.460
Coming through!

31:27.400 --> 31:28.140
Excuse me.

31:29.590 --> 31:30.090
Hello,

31:30.160 --> 31:30.980
have you seen this?

31:32.030 --> 31:32.770
No, I haven't.

31:33.720 --> 31:34.660
Have you seen this?

31:36.380 --> 31:42.180
♪I'd be the waves, just to carry you away...♪

31:44.350 --> 31:45.660
Have you seen this?

31:47.030 --> 31:47.770
No.

31:47.920 --> 31:48.460
Have you seen this?

31:49.270 --> 31:49.900
No.

31:50.590 --> 31:51.420
There, there!

31:55.160 --> 31:55.810
Be good now.

31:56.920 --> 31:57.900
Mother will be right back.

32:02.880 --> 32:03.290
Come here,

32:03.680 --> 32:04.460
give me a hand.

32:05.200 --> 32:05.980
He needs to eat his porridge.

32:06.960 --> 32:07.490
Easy now.

32:08.480 --> 32:08.860
There, there.

32:09.400 --> 32:10.220
Porridge is coming!

32:10.830 --> 32:11.290
Come on.

32:16.000 --> 32:16.570
Come on.

32:17.110 --> 32:17.770
Be good now.

32:19.160 --> 32:20.490
Mother's back, isn't she?

32:27.540 --> 32:33.460
♪If you're the moon, I'll be falling snow♪

32:34.580 --> 32:41.340
♪Let them chase the skies, I'll stay with you below♪

32:41.620 --> 32:47.500
♪I miss the sweetness in your smile so true♪

32:47.780 --> 32:48.380
♪So please♪

32:48.660 --> 32:53.500
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view...♪

32:53.510 --> 32:54.090
Easy now.

32:54.860 --> 32:55.460
♪So please...♪

32:55.880 --> 32:56.660
We're back!

32:57.590 --> 32:58.620
- Mother! - Go to your mother.

33:01.900 --> 33:02.540
♪So please♪

33:02.740 --> 33:12.580
♪Don't say goodbye before the sun fades from view♪

33:32.310 --> 33:33.470
He's actually a demon!

33:34.680 --> 33:35.730
I found out last night.

33:36.350 --> 33:37.320
He's from the Chameleon Snake clan.

33:37.640 --> 33:39.480
They change color to blend in.

33:40.510 --> 33:41.800
They're masters of concealment.

33:44.480 --> 33:44.980
Man Man,

33:45.510 --> 33:46.660
you got an itch or what?

33:54.480 --> 33:55.980
Da Ji and the other victims

33:56.590 --> 33:57.700
were all killed by snake venom.

33:59.440 --> 34:00.380
Leave it to me.

34:18.760 --> 34:19.650
I'm not the killer.

34:20.840 --> 34:21.740
I came to Aodeng

34:21.760 --> 34:23.130
only to find the Star Stone.

34:24.230 --> 34:25.490
I haven't killed anyone.

34:30.630 --> 34:31.850
So it's not him?

34:36.440 --> 34:37.500
Forget everything,

34:38.030 --> 34:38.980
leave Aodeng,

34:39.710 --> 34:41.270
and never come back.

35:02.710 --> 35:03.860
If it's not him,

35:04.280 --> 35:05.170
then who could it be?

35:06.880 --> 35:07.820
Snake venom...

35:13.800 --> 35:15.820
Don't tell me it's you, Little Nine?

35:33.280 --> 35:33.980
Relax.

35:35.110 --> 35:36.130
The blood didn't turn black.

35:36.840 --> 35:37.530
Looks like

35:38.280 --> 35:39.010
it's not Little Nine.

35:44.370 --> 35:47.260
Our delicate and precious Master Chi Wen

35:47.440 --> 35:49.250
testing the poison in my place?

35:49.750 --> 35:51.300
I'm so touched.

35:56.960 --> 35:57.900
Are you Ji Ling?

36:02.510 --> 36:03.780
You're so obsessed with Ji Ling?

36:04.840 --> 36:06.460
You have to prove I'm him?

36:10.280 --> 36:11.690
Even if Ji Ling is a puppet,

36:12.840 --> 36:14.460
where did his South Mountain fox memories

36:14.460 --> 36:15.300
come from?

36:16.320 --> 36:17.300
Fake memories

36:17.880 --> 36:19.610
don't have that many details.

36:26.150 --> 36:26.820
What are you doing?

36:28.320 --> 36:30.090
Trying to know your secret.

36:32.280 --> 36:34.300
Indeed a defenseless boy.

36:35.070 --> 36:36.260
You have no sacred power now.

36:36.440 --> 36:37.740
You can't resist my Word Magic.

36:38.670 --> 36:39.820
What a perfect chance.

36:40.110 --> 36:40.900
How could I waste it?

36:41.230 --> 36:42.130
I suggest you stop.

36:43.230 --> 36:44.690
If you dare disrespect me,

36:45.400 --> 36:45.980
I'll...

36:46.880 --> 36:47.380
I'll...

36:47.400 --> 36:48.170
What?

36:51.070 --> 36:52.420
With that expression,

36:53.920 --> 36:55.570
you're just asking for it.

37:04.000 --> 37:04.820
Where is my magic?

37:09.050 --> 37:09.820
You can't seem

37:10.920 --> 37:12.130
to control your power too.

37:13.780 --> 37:15.090
Even if you use Word Magic,

37:16.070 --> 37:17.690
my answer won't change.

37:18.400 --> 37:19.260
I am not Ji Ling.

37:22.360 --> 37:23.460
But just now...

37:25.760 --> 37:26.740
I tested the poison for you

37:27.150 --> 37:27.980
because I knew

37:28.150 --> 37:29.050
I'd be fine.

37:30.230 --> 37:31.900
The killer's target is the Star Stone.

37:32.840 --> 37:33.650
All the victims

37:34.190 --> 37:35.420
were people who loved Di Zhu.

37:35.840 --> 37:36.260
Di Zhu,

37:36.880 --> 37:37.690
I won't give up on you!

37:38.150 --> 37:39.420
You and the Star Stone are both mine!

37:42.000 --> 37:42.940
Figured it out?

37:44.440 --> 37:45.210
Yeah.

37:46.360 --> 37:47.830
If the killer means

37:47.920 --> 37:49.820
to eliminate competitors for the Star Stone,

37:50.070 --> 37:50.950
then Man Man

37:51.960 --> 37:53.820
should be his primary target.

37:55.480 --> 37:56.980
Snake venom can kill mortals,

37:57.480 --> 37:58.570
but it can't kill demons.

37:59.550 --> 38:00.210
Exactly.

38:00.670 --> 38:02.170
Even if Little Nine were the killer,

38:03.000 --> 38:04.690
its venom couldn't kill me.

38:05.510 --> 38:06.300
So...

38:07.000 --> 38:08.340
I dared to test it for you.

38:44.320 --> 38:45.300
How's it going on your end?

38:46.840 --> 38:47.820
People keep dying,

38:48.440 --> 38:48.860
and

38:49.190 --> 38:49.900
no killer found.

38:50.630 --> 38:51.940
Ao Erlie returns tonight.

38:52.630 --> 38:53.340
You need to hurry.

38:55.710 --> 38:56.340
I know.

38:58.230 --> 38:59.570
Why are you so quiet today?

39:00.230 --> 39:02.420
Acting all solemn and mature.

39:02.920 --> 39:03.930
Do the girls of Aodeng

39:04.550 --> 39:06.010
like this cold attitude?

39:09.000 --> 39:10.460
The more on my mind,

39:11.440 --> 39:12.850
the less I feel like talking.

39:13.880 --> 39:14.610
Look at you,

39:14.920 --> 39:15.690
so relaxed.

39:16.030 --> 39:16.690
What are you folding?

39:18.320 --> 39:19.610
My younger brother was always sickly,

39:20.510 --> 39:21.490
and stayed home all the time.

39:22.840 --> 39:24.530
He folded paper lanterns in all sorts of shapes.

39:25.400 --> 39:26.170
Did you forget?

39:28.280 --> 39:29.050
Of course I remember.

39:29.880 --> 39:30.570
He taught you how

39:30.800 --> 39:31.940
to make these paper lanterns, right?

39:34.670 --> 39:36.450
Whenever I miss him,

39:37.070 --> 39:38.260
I fold one.

39:39.280 --> 39:40.090
Di Zhu,

39:40.920 --> 39:42.300
how can you be so happy now?

39:43.280 --> 39:44.810
If the real killer isn't caught in three days,

39:45.280 --> 39:46.900
you and Man Man will be burned alive.

39:51.280 --> 39:52.090
Yeah.

39:53.070 --> 39:53.860
"Live together, die together"?

39:54.550 --> 39:56.260
That's just a story to fool girls.

39:57.030 --> 39:57.940
I don't like him

39:59.230 --> 40:01.260
enough to die for him.

40:03.600 --> 40:05.340
Being burned alive

40:05.340 --> 40:06.450
with someone so cold?

40:07.790 --> 40:08.460
That's way too tragic.

40:10.510 --> 40:11.690
We're worlds apart.

40:13.400 --> 40:13.820
No way.

40:17.800 --> 40:18.460
Di Zhu!

40:18.630 --> 40:19.620
The chieftain is back.

40:19.630 --> 40:20.420
He's asking for you!

40:24.880 --> 40:25.710
Okay.

40:26.440 --> 40:27.310
Got it.

40:38.300 --> 40:39.460
♪It's your light♪

40:39.660 --> 40:41.540
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

40:41.700 --> 40:44.820
♪That set the night alight♪

40:45.180 --> 40:51.700
♪And lead me through the fight♪

40:53.460 --> 40:55.340
♪Jade in the lake, sand in my hand♪

40:55.780 --> 41:00.220
♪Let bitter seeds grow, let fate bloom♪

41:01.020 --> 41:02.700
♪Face in the mirror, veiled in mist♪

41:02.860 --> 41:08.260
♪Till snow has kissed dark hair to white♪

41:09.020 --> 41:14.420
♪Night lamp burning by the old table♪

41:16.740 --> 41:22.780
♪Stitch by stitch, mending moonlight♪

41:23.740 --> 41:25.900
♪The dancing light, the shattered wave♪

41:26.180 --> 41:31.020
♪Are all my helpless, drifting haze♪

41:31.380 --> 41:33.700
♪The boiling frost, the stubborn stare♪

41:33.900 --> 41:38.980
♪Are all the pride I'll never wear♪

41:39.220 --> 41:41.220
♪Your shoulder, your tear-bright eyes♪

41:41.500 --> 41:45.860
♪Are the strength that lifts my dreams to the skies♪

41:46.860 --> 41:53.820
♪Stay with me, let's gaze above♪

42:10.380 --> 42:13.340
♪Nowhere to rest, nowhere to hide♪

42:14.420 --> 42:17.820
♪Bare in body yet boundless inside♪

42:18.620 --> 42:21.140
♪Nothing to seek, nothing to erase♪

42:21.380 --> 42:24.460
♪Like water gone, like the formless moon♪

42:24.860 --> 42:27.180
♪Let every dream and wild desire♪

42:27.700 --> 42:32.100
♪Forge the edge that lifts us higher♪

42:32.340 --> 42:34.500
♪Bells through endless time, sun and moon alike in shine♪

42:34.900 --> 42:39.860
♪Love and hate all earn their crown♪

42:40.100 --> 42:41.260
♪It's your light♪

42:41.460 --> 42:43.300
♪Your storms, your watchful eyes♪

42:43.500 --> 42:46.620
♪That set the night alight♪

42:47.380 --> 42:56.820
♪And lead me sailing afar♪
